---
title: Shawarma-Spiced Chicken with Pomegranate, Dried Apricots and Roasted Carrots
description: Fresh fruity flavours meet tender, savoury spiced chicken in this dish. Bulgur and parsley bring the flavours of tabuleh while the our shawarma spice blend tops of the dish for a fun riff on one of our favourite take-out meals.
